使用插图：<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zzzzzac" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5215451); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5215451&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606781512" alt="ZZZZZac" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5215451)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zzzzzac" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5215451); return false;">ZZZZZac</a></span>在画廊上传的<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/gallery/zac04">此图片</a></p>
